<div class="item-separator HPHideBox item1"></div>
<article class="FpFeaturedBoxWrap HPHideBox article ">
	<div class="contentBoxWrap">
		<div class="contentWrap">
							<figure class="featuredArticleImage"><a href="/spirit/spiritual-growth/6347-10-signs-that-you-re-captive-to-the-enemy"><img src="http://cdn.charismamag.com/templates/charisma_mag/images/blank.gif" data-src="http://cdn.charismamag.com/images/archives/articles/Blogs/The-Plumb-Line/demonic-strategies.jpg" alt="man with hands over eyes" width="263" height="145" title="man with hands over eyes"></a></figure>
						<h1><a href="/spirit/spiritual-growth/6347-10-signs-that-you-re-captive-to-the-enemy">10 Signs That You're Captive to the Enemy</a></h1>
			<div class="contentBody"><p>So many people allow negative experiences and broken dreams to stop them. Yet God has the power to propel you beyond your disappointments.</p></div>
		</div>
